summary: Diff adds numeric normalization utilities (BigInt->number, timestamp conversion), updates React Query entitlements hook to return normalized numbers, updates Generate gating/UI to use those numbers, stabilizes generated outputs rendering, and adds a manual QA checklist. Backend is also modified around profiles/subscription status and proposal structures.

hallucinated_features.description: Backend data model changes to SavedProposal to include a unique numeric `id` and introduction of `nextProposalId` plus a nested saved-proposals map keyed by proposal id.
hallucinated_features.reason: BuildRequest focuses on fixing the Generate crash and numeric/type issues; it does not request changes to the proposal persistence model/identifier scheme.
